Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}找您花了不少工夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}这里没有足够的医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}虽然只是照猫画虎，但总比没有好
